OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Forever chemicals' limited
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin US tap water            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The US has imposed its first nationwide
OL,6, limits on several harmful chemicals    
OL,7, found in tap water across the country. 
OL,9,FResearch suggests millions of Americans
OL,10,Flikely drink water contaminated with   
OL,11,FPFAS chemicals, which are linked to a  
OL,12,Fhost of health issues including cancer.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, officials finalised a    
OL,15,Frule that requires local governments to
OL,16,Fremove six versions of the chemicals   
OL,17,Ffrom water systems.                    
OL,19,FThe government has allocated an extra  
OL,20,F$1bn (#794m) to help cover the costs.  
